{"tid":404640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華56歲生日笑聲不斷 吳君如鄭中基齊賀","createTime":"2017-09-18T09:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:11:47.000Z","uid":22869,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c4100144de52e02a17543b88346c334cc2ad71","tid":404640,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】劉德華（華仔）於本月27日56歲生日，今年初他經歷墮馬受傷意外，令粉絲擔心。前晚華仔出席華仔天地為他舉行的生日派對，還有圈中好友吳君如、鄭中基、羅蘭等到賀，共度開心一晚。華仔感受到粉絲的心意，昨日凌晨在官網留言表示感謝：「一家人，笑聲不斷！夢中再次相見！」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n華仔視為「親生仔」的Andox與黑仔的微博分享派對照片，留言：「今年的生日會在一片笑聲下順利完成了（實在真的超不捨）。台上，華阿媽精神滿滿、蹦蹦跳跳的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/170905_a6f72a8b363bfd3db961efb0e7f358cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F170905_a6f72a8b363bfd3db961efb0e7f358cc.jpg&h=5c7b121e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00016/1505671392507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00016%2F1505671392507&d=Y8qSumg6seHukszPxWBdZcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=17135e9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00016%2F1505671392507&h=7fcc2934\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00016/1505671392507</a>"}]}